WEREN'T YOU THE FLIGHT ATTENDANT

19:45.749 --> 19:46.750
ON THAT AIR NEW ZEALAND FLIGHT?

19:46.881 --> 19:48.099
THAT'S RIGHT.

19:48.230 --> 19:49.884
TALK ABOUT COINCIDENCES.

19:50.014 --> 19:51.320
OH, IT GETS BETTER.

19:51.451 --> 19:54.758
I DON'T KNOW YOUR NAME,
BUT YOU'RE JAKE BARNES.

19:54.889 --> 19:56.891
ERIC TOLD ME TO EXPECT YOU.

19:57.021 --> 19:58.371
I'M ALLIE REESE.

19:59.981 --> 20:01.417
I WAS CLAIRE'S BEST FRIEND.

20:06.117 --> 20:07.858
HEY, YOU KNOW TERRY, MY SON?

20:07.989 --> 20:09.208
