20:21.742 --> 20:23.700
AND WHAT DOES HE KNOW ABOUT ME?

20:23.831 --> 20:25.485
I DON'T KNOW.

20:26.616 --> 20:28.096
DID CLAIRE EVER TALK ABOUT ME?

20:28.227 --> 20:29.140
YES.

20:29.271 --> 20:31.230
AND, WHAT DID SHE SAY?

20:32.927 --> 20:34.755
THOSE WERE
PRIVATE CONVERSATIONS.

20:36.496 --> 20:37.584
DOES HE KNOW I'M COMING?

20:38.498 --> 20:39.542
YES HE DOES.

20:42.806 --> 20:46.767
[ENERGETIC MUSIC PLAYING]

21:22.890 --> 21:25.545
WOW, WHAT A SIGHT.

21:32.291 --> 21:33.901
WHAT DID YOU SAY?

21:34.031 --> 21:36.686
THE CITY FROM HERE,
IT'S AMAZING.

21:36.817 --> 21:38.471
IT'S THE BEST WAY TO SEE IT.

21:40.690 --> 21:42.475
THAT LOOKS LIKE AN OLD FORT.

21:42.605 --> 21:44.694
IT IS, IT'S FORT DENISON,

21:44.825 --> 21:46.696
IT DATES BACK
TO THE CONVICT SHIPS.

21:46.827 --> 21:47.741
WOW.

21:49.090 --> 21:51.048
IT'S ALL A LITTLE UNBELIEVABLE,
DON'T YOU THINK?

21:51.179 --> 21:52.833
I MEAN, FIRST YOU'RE
ON THE AIR NEW ZEALAND FLIGHT,

21:52.963 --> 21:54.704
THEN YOU'RE A FRIEND
OF JAKE'S WIFE,

21:54.835 --> 21:56.315
AND NOW YOU'RE FLYING HIM
TO MEET HIS SON?

21:56.445 --> 21:58.665
I MEAN, WHAT ARE THE ODDS
OF THAT HAPPENING?

21:58.795 --> 22:00.536
SOME OF THE NATIVE PEOPLE

22:00.667 --> 22:02.712
WOULDN'T THINK
IT STRANGE AT ALL.

22:02.843 --> 22:04.497
THEY BELIEVE HEAVEN
AND EARTH WILL MOVE AS ONE

22:04.627 --> 22:06.020
TO PROTECT A CHILD.

22:06.150 --> 22:08.936
SO, MAYBE I'VE BEEN CHOSEN
TO GET YOU SAFELY TO AVALON,

22:09.066 --> 22:12.809
IN WHICH CASE IT'S PROVIDENCE,
NOT COINCIDENCE.

22:12.940 --> 22:14.463
I LIKE THAT.

22:16.596 --> 22:17.858
SYDNEY HARBOUR SEAPLANES

22:23.646 --> 22:24.995
THAT'S WHERE WE'RE GOING,

22:25.126 --> 22:27.389
THAT'S AVALON.

22:27.520 --> 22:28.738
WHAT'S GOING ON?

22:28.869 --> 22:31.001
IT'S A SURF CARNIVAL WITH TEAMS
FROM THE BEACHES

22:31.132 --> 22:32.481
AROUND NEW SOUTH WALES.

22:32.612 --> 22:34.135
IF YOU EVER WANT
TO SEE SOMETHING

22:34.265 --> 22:36.920
UNIQUELY AUSTRALIAN THOUGH,
THIS IS IT.

22:37.051 --> 22:40.881
